programme.title: Simfoni Alam Ep3
programme.desc: Sang Penjaga Hutan - Taman Negeri Royal Belum terletak di utara hujung Perak. Luas kawasan bagi hutan simpanan ini dilaporkan meliputi seluas 300, 000 hektar. Hutan Belum ini dibahagikan kepada bahagian atas dan bahagian bawah. Bahagian atas hutan belum ini ditutupi oleh 117, 500 hektar kawasan hutan yang tebal dan memasuki sempadan Thailand-Malaysia. Renjer adalah barisan hadapan (frontliner) yang bertindak sebagai benteng bagi membanteras pencerobohan untuk melindungi biodiversiti; jurucakap kepada flora dan fauna; serta guru bagi mendidik orang awam untuk mengenali dan menghargai biodiversiti. Mereka adalah sokongan teknikal untuk badan awam dalam projek memperbaiki alam sekitar. Mereka menjalankan laporan, kajian dan mengambil bahagian dalam perunding projek-projek ini untuk memperbaikipersekitaran.

programme.title: Syurgaku Tak Sempurna S1 Ep06
programme.desc: Tengku Zarif dan Zalia bernikah di luar negara.Tengku Kamal dan Tengku Zaharah mengamuk bila dapat tahu mereka bernikah.Tengku Kamal suruh anaknya ceraikan Zalia tapi dibangkang keras oleh Tengku Zarif.Demi menjaga nama keluarga majlis resepsi secara sederhana diadakan.Tengku Zaharah sangat kecewa dengan Tengku Zarif.Zalia menjemput ayahnya datang ke majlis mereka tetapi Zahid bagi alasan tak sihat dan tidak mahu hadir.Zalia sedih yang teramat kerana tidak diterima di dalam keluarga oleh mereka.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep07
programme.desc: Tugas pertama Ezgi di La Gabbia ialah menganjurkan malam Latin. Serdar juga akan hadir dalam organisasi ini dan bersedia untuk tango dengan Ezgi. Tetapi Ezgi terpaksa belajar tango untuk masa yang singkat kerana dia tidak tahu menarinya dan membohongi Serdar mengenainya. zgr, yang mahir dalam tango, menawarkan untuk membantu Ezgi dalam perkara ini. Walaupun Ezgi dan zgr, yang semakin rapat semasa berlatih bersama, dipengaruhi oleh satu sama lain, kehadiran Yesim dan Serdar menghalang mereka daripada menyatakan perkara ini. Sementara itu, penampilan Soner akan mengelirukan segala-galanya, dan apa yang berlaku malam ini akan menyebabkan zgr dan Ezgi membuka lembaran baru dalam hubungan mereka.

programme.title: Japanizi Going Going Gong Ep23
programme.desc: Japanizi Going Going Gong ialah pertunjukan permainan fizikal kanak-kanak Kanada dengan motif Jepun di mana peserta bersaing dengan rakan sepasukan menentang pasukan lain semasa mereka menangani halangan dan cabaran untuk menguji keupayaan mental, kekuatan, ketahanan dan kepintaran mereka.

programme.title: Interview Jodoh
programme.desc: SAFURA, seorang gadis cantik dan bergaya, hantu aiskrim,suka melihat menara Eiffel dan terlalu sibuk dengan urusan kerjanya di sebuah syarikat di ibu kota. Dia mempunyai tabiat buruk iaitu suka membuang batang aiskrim merata-rata tempat. Persoalan yang sering dipertanyakan kepadanya tentang teman lelaki dan jodoh membuat dia berasa tertekan. Melihat rakan-rakannya yang lain sudah berkahwin dan memiliki teman lelaki, dia mencari jalan untuk memilih lelaki yang sesuai untuk dijadikan teman lelaki. IMRAN dan ADIB merupakan sahabat baik sejak dari kecil yang sedang mencari pekerjaan. Imran, kacak, bergaya, namun agak nakal dan kurang bijak berbanding Adib. Dia dibuang kerja kerana tidak dapat fokus pekerjaan akibat putus cinta. Adib pula sentiasa merendah diri, memiliki hobi mengumbul batang aiskrim, berpendidikan, kurang bergaya berbanding Imran, penyabar dan seorang yang pendiam kerana suka memendam perasaan. Imran dan Adib menghadiri satu temuduga di sebuah syarikat untuk mencari pekerjaan, namun temuduga itu berubah kepada temuduga jodoh yang diuruskan oleh Safura untuk mencari teman lelaki.

programme.title: Saat Hati Telah Memilih Ep06
programme.desc: Andi minta restu Papa Riri untuk menikahi Riri. Papa Riri merestui tapi dengan syarat. Andi pun bertekad untuk sembuh dan memutuskan untuk mengikuti kemauan Iren pergi ke Amerika secepatnya. Sementara Haris yang mengikuti Andi melihat sikap Riri ke Andi dan sadar kalau Riri benar-benar menyayangi Andi. Tanti mengenalkan Iren dan Sinta yang tidak sengaja bertemu. Iren bilang Tanti pacar Haris ke Sinta yang tadinya ingin menjodohkan Tanti dengan Arman.

programme.title: Kaki Bahan S6 Ep01
programme.desc: Kaki Bahan merupakan sebuah rancangan komedi yang akan berkongsikan video-video popular lagi lucu dengan caranya tersendiri.

programme.title: Anggun Mikayla Ep11
programme.desc: Perjalanan hidup Mikayla sentiasa bersimpang-siur dengan dugaan sejak dia mencelikkan mata birunya ke dunia. Status kelahirannya membuatkan dia seringkali menerima cacian penduduk kampung dan menjadi mangsa buli semasa kecil. Mekap adalah cara Mikayla menidakkan kewujudannya sendiri. Dia berselindung di sebalik rambut palsu hitam untuk menyorokkan rambut auburnnya serta mengenakan pelbagai jenis mekap untuk menggelapkan warna kulit kerana keinginannya untuk tampak Melayu. Siang, Mikayla bekerja sebagai jurumekap artis dan apabila malam tiba, dia menjelma sebagai pontianak. Pertemuan Mikayla dengan Idriz dalam satu insiden lucu telah mencipta satu hubungan aneh yang tidak bernama. Dalam diam, Idriz menyimpan rasa tetapi keinginannya terbatas kerana tanggungjawabnya pada keluarga. Jurugambar yang bekerja bersamanya, Asif yang suka mengusik Mikayla mulai tersedar yang usikannya sudah bertukar menjadi perasaan sebenar. Tetapi, dia terlajak memikat pelakon popular bernama Andria, sebelum tersedar tentang perasaannya terhadap Mikayla. Sedang Mikayla dalam keadaan celaru, lelaki dari masa silamnya, Aidan pula muncul kembali, menagih kemaafan kerana meninggalkan parut panjang di dahinya. Aidan yang kini sudah bergelar pelakon popular cuba memadamkan kenangan sakit mereka demi merebut hati yang dirinduinya itu. Tetapi, impian Mikayla hanya satu, berhadapan dengan masa silamnya dan mencantas kebencian mama. Cinta bukan destinasi yang diimpi. Namun, hatinya terus menjadi buruan oleh tiga orang lelaki.

programme.title: Tok Guru Ep03
programme.desc: Tok Guru Nik Ahmad ajak Cikgu Roslan mengajar ilmu alam di pondoknya. Che mat sakit hati dpat tahu Nik Naimah mula rapat dengan Cikgu Roslan. Che Mat buat fitnah Tok Guru tukar sistem pengajian pondok dengan masukkan matapelajaran yang diajar cikgu Roslan guna tulisan rumi dan bukan tulisan Jawi. Tok Guru Wan Ismail dan Tok Guru Mustapa hasil maklumat Che mat tuduh Tok Guru Nik Ahmad degil, keras kepala dan gedebe kerana nak tukar tradisi pengajian pondok.

Ji Kyung membantu Se Mi bertemu Woo Joo secara rahsia tetapi Woo Joo tidak berasa selesa apabila dia bersama ibunya.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep23
programme.desc: Memaparkan Nizam bertemu Suraya dan mengugutnya, kemudiannya Nizam ditikam dan jatuh terhentak kepalanya dan tidak sedarkan diri, kini berada di wad hospital. Mizan dan Hani melawatnya dan Sheila yang merungut banyak dugaannya ditenang oleh Hani. Sebelum itu Sheila yang mengiringi ibunya ke rumah (selepas discharge) berterus terang situasinya dengan Nizam dan mengakui keluarga Nizam amat baik. Ibu Sheila kelihatan menerima hakikat merestuinya. Sementara Sheila terus menemani Nizam yang masih tidak sedarkan diri, dia juga merayu dan meratapi akan kelakuan dan kesilapan lalunya dan kesal. Hani dan Mizan singgah berbual di kedai minuman, Hani kebetulan terjumpa sahabat karibnya Kalsom dan menceritakan kepada Mizan, semasa inilah Mizan berubah dan bertanya Hani yang tidak pernah menceritakan hubungannya dengan Shariff. Hani menjelaskan segalanya dan merayu memujuk Mizan yang kelihatan merajuk pula. Sebenarnya semasa Nizam bersemuka dan berbual dengan Suraya, Nizam merakam dan dia memajukan kepada Hani. Ini membuatkan Hani dan Mizan ketahui. Mereka berdua bergegas menemui Nizam, walau pun dia mulai sedar tetapi ingatannya masih terganggu. Sementara itu apa yang dilakukan Dato Fuad telah dibayangi Datin Umairah. Datin Umairah terus tenang dan berdiam tetapi meminta Shariff terus bertindak.

programme.title: Permainan Cinta S1 Ep11
programme.desc: Syifa dan Safiah rasa bersalah bila dapat tahu Malik telah curi formula kosmetik itu dari Dr Arman. Mereka juga dapat tahu yang Dr Arman bakal disaman oleh klien kerana telah hilangkan formula itu. Syifa dan Safiah bertemu dengan Dr Arman untuk minta maaf tetapi ketika pertemuan itu, Dr Arman telah serahkan mereka kepada PI Razlan dan Dato Hajidi dan Dr Arman tidak mahu berjumpa dengan mereka lagi. Dato Hajidi mahu Syifa dan Safiah serahkan kembali wang yang mereka telah ditipu, jika tidak Syifa dan Safiah akan diserahkan kepada polis. Syifa dan Safiah setuju untuk kembalikan duit Dato Hajidi. Safiah dan Syifakembali ke kehidupan asal mereka. Syifa tanya kepada Safiah kenapa tinggalkan makmal tempohari. Safiah beritahu yang dia tak sampai hati nak tipu Dr Arman telah pilih Safiah kerana dia benar benar jatuh cinta pada Dr Arman.Syifa beritahu Safiah ang Dr Arman telah pilih Safiah kerana gambar dia di wallpaper tempohari. Safiah rasa bersalah dan ingin bertemu Dr Arman untuk betulkan keadaan.

programme.title: Permainan Cinta S1 Ep12
programme.desc: Syifa dan Safiah upah PI Razlan untuk bantu mereka merampas semula formula itu. Mereka menunggu peluang yang sesuai untuk mulakan operasi.Jamal teruja untuk uruskan syarikat sepeninggalan Malik ke luar negara. Syifa dan Safiah menyamar menjadi model untuk iklan kosmetik untuk iklan komersial syarikat Malik. Mereka gunakan kecantikan serta kebodohan Jamal untuk pikat Jamal sehingga membuatkan Jamal percayakan mereka. PI Razlan bertemu Jamal dan perkenalkan diri sebagai polis yang sedang siasat Syifa dan Safiah. PI Razlan dedahkan kepada Jamal yang Safiah dan Syifa ingin mencuri formula kosmetik tetapi Jamal tidak percaya.

programme.title: Sesalan Terakhir
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Natasha merupakan anak tidak sah taraf. Hidupnya tidak seperti orang lain. Dia dipinggirkan orang kampung kerana sikap ibunya, Auni, yang sering menjalinkan hubungan dengan lelaki kaya kerana ingin memiliki kekayaan. Puas Natasha menasihati ibunya supaya kembali ke jalan yang benar.

programme.title: Tok Guru Ep03
programme.desc: Tok Guru Nik Ahmad ajak Cikgu Roslan mengajar ilmu alam di pondoknya. Che mat sakit hati dpat tahu Nik Naimah mula rapat dengan Cikgu Roslan. Che Mat buat fitnah Tok Guru tukar sistem pengajian pondok dengan masukkan matapelajaran yang diajar cikgu Roslan guna tulisan rumi dan bukan tulisan Jawi. Tok Guru Wan Ismail dan Tok Guru Mustapa hasil maklumat Che mat tuduh Tok Guru Nik Ahmad degil, keras kepala dan gedebe kerana nak tukar tradisi pengajian pondok.

programme.title: Saat Hati Telah Memilih Ep22
programme.desc: Tanti gelisah karena Haris belum juga pulang ke rumah dan ia juga takut Haris akan menceraikannya. Iren berusaha menghibur Tanti dengan meyakinkan dia bahwa Haris pasti pulang dan tidak akan menceraikannya. Tiba-tiba bel berbunyi dan mereka menduga Haris yang datang. Tetapi ternyata Arya yang datang. Arya langsung menarik tangan Tanti dan akan membawanya ke kantor polisi karena ia menganggap Tanti yang mencelakakan Riri. Iren berusaha menghalangi Arya yang akan membawa Tanti. Akhirnya Tanti mengakui bahwa ia yang mencelakai Riri tetapi ia berdalih tidak sengaja, dan dia beralasan dia merasa cemburu karena Haris menemui Riri.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep08
programme.desc: Keakraban antara Ezgi dan zgr terganggu dengan kedatangan Serdar dan Yesim. Serdar tidak selesa dengan minat zgr terhadap Ezgi dan bersama-sama Yesim mula mempersoalkan keadaan ini. Deniz mula-mula menyedari perasaan Ezgi terhadap zgr dan memberi amaran kepada Ezgi supaya tidak melakukan kesilapan. Ozan menyedari perasaan zgr terhadap Ezgi dan menyokongnya dalam hal ini. Ibu mereka, yang tidak mahu kedua-duanya berkumpul, juga mengambil tindakan dan memutuskan untuk melakukan apa sahaja untuk memisahkan mereka.

programme.desc: ARLISA, merupakan seorang pelajar kolej yang sedang bercinta dengan seorang lelaki bernama Nazri sejak dibangku sekolah lagi. Arlisa menyambung pengajiannya di sebuah universiti semata untuk mengejar impiannya menjadi seorang wartawan. Hubungan yang terjalin sudah menjangkau enam tahun dan hubungan mereka tidak pernah goyah dek kerana orang ketiga. Mereka saling sayang menyayangi dan sangat setia. Malangnya, Nazri seorang lelaki yang panas baran, mudah melenting dan suka memarahi Arlisa hanya disebabkan perkara yang kecil.

Iren semakin benci dengan Riri sementara Nurdin ingin memanfaatkan situasi ini untuk membuat Andi membenci Riri. Haris juga terpaksa harus berbohong ke Karin kalau Riri adalah pacarnya untuk balas dendam. Tanti mengira Haris pacar Riri karena melihat Haris menggendong Riri yang terjatuh.

programme.title: Anggun Mikayla Ep12
programme.desc: Perjalanan hidup Mikayla sentiasa bersimpang-siur dengan dugaan sejak dia mencelikkan mata birunya ke dunia. Status kelahirannya membuatkan dia seringkali menerima cacian penduduk kampung dan menjadi mangsa buli semasa kecil. Mekap adalah cara Mikayla menidakkan kewujudannya sendiri. Dia berselindung di sebalik rambut palsu hitam untuk menyorokkan rambut auburnnya serta mengenakan pelbagai jenis mekap untuk menggelapkan warna kulit kerana keinginannya untuk tampak Melayu. Siang, Mikayla bekerja sebagai jurumekap artis dan apabila malam tiba, dia menjelma sebagai pontianak. Pertemuan Mikayla dengan Idriz dalam satu insiden lucu telah mencipta satu hubungan aneh yang tidak bernama. Dalam diam, Idriz menyimpan rasa tetapi keinginannya terbatas kerana tanggungjawabnya pada keluarga. Jurugambar yang bekerja bersamanya, Asif yang suka mengusik Mikayla mulai tersedar yang usikannya sudah bertukar menjadi perasaan sebenar. Tetapi, dia terlajak memikat pelakon popular bernama Andria, sebelum tersedar tentang perasaannya terhadap Mikayla. Sedang Mikayla dalam keadaan celaru, lelaki dari masa silamnya, Aidan pula muncul kembali, menagih kemaafan kerana meninggalkan parut panjang di dahinya. Aidan yang kini sudah bergelar pelakon popular cuba memadamkan kenangan sakit mereka demi merebut hati yang dirinduinya itu. Tetapi, impian Mikayla hanya satu, berhadapan dengan masa silamnya dan mencantas kebencian mama. Cinta bukan destinasi yang diimpi. Namun, hatinya terus menjadi buruan oleh tiga orang lelaki.

programme.desc: Filem ini membawa penonton ke era zaman lampau iaitu sebelum abad ke-19 tetapi kisah yang dipaparkan berkaitan dengan masyarakat Malaysia hari ini. Ia mengisahkan tiga orang pemuda - Gunung, Daik dan Bercabang - yang melarikan diri daripada menjadi hamba abdi kepada Orang Kaya Seri Bentan. Mereka bertiga berhenti di sebuah kota bernama Lang Buana di pinggir sebuah sungai. Setibanya di kota itu, mereka disambut meriah kerana disangka putera raja yang dapat menyelamatkan kota itu daripada serangan Sang Nira. Terperangkap oleh keadaan, ketiga-tiga pemuda berkenaan terpaksa menyamar menjadi putera raja dan merangka taktik peperangan bagi memperkuatkan benteng pertahanan Lang Buana.

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep06
programme.desc: Zulkarnain pernah terkilan kerana familinya ada merancang untuk menjodohkannya dengan Farah, namun Farah pula dinikahi Lukman sebagai ganti tikar. Lukman mempertikaikan tindakan Farah yang menghilangkan diri selama beberapa hari tanpa memberitahunya. Farah membidas Lukman yang culas amanah sebagai suami. Lebih menyakitkan hati apabila Lukman menuduhnya sengaja balik kampung untuk bertemu dengan skandalnya, Nazim. Perbalahan mereka berakhir apabila Lukman menunaikan tanggungjawabnya sebagai suami. Farah mula menikmati manisnya perkahwinan dan mula merasai saat bahagia bersama Lukman. Kebahagiaan mereka membuatkan cemburu Myra makin marak. Farah minta izin daripada Lukman untuk mula bekerja di syarikat kenalan famili

programme.title: Penunggu Simpang

Penunggu Simpang ini menyerupai wanita yang sangat cantik berambut panjang hingga ke tanah. Senyumannya menyebabkan sesiapa yang terserempak menjadi sangat takut.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep24
programme.desc: Memaparkan Nizam keluar wad serta di terima baik ibu Sheila. Sheila meminta Nizam bersabar kerana dia perlu memantau kesihatan dan menyambung urusan kerja perniagaan bapanya. Semasa berkereta, Sheila ternampak Hani bersama Shariff dan mengambil gambar. Sheila tidak tahu menahu Shariff terpaksa mencari dan menemui Hani kerana ingin memberitahu dan menyampaikan hasil siasatan DNA bahawa mereka dua beradik. Hani masih sangsi dan mengarapkan pengesahan lagi. Shariff pula terpaksa bergegas berkaitan siasatan skandal Dato Fuad dan Suraya dan Hani ingin membantunya dituruti Kalsom (penyiasat upahan Shariff). Sheila pula memajukan gambar itu kepada Nizam agar jangan lagi mengharap Hani. Terdahulu Mizan meluahkan rasa hatinya kepada Dzul, dia ingin berhenti kerja berikutan sikap isterinya yang berbaik dengan Shariff. Semasa Shariff, Hani dan Kalsom tiba di bawah bangunan di mana Dato Fuad dan Suraya berada, bapa Shariff juga tiba dan dia terus bersama penguatkuasa Jabatan Ugama semasa Dato Fuad dan Suraya ditahan. Kemudiannya ketika Datin Umairah bersama Shariff, bapa Shariff (abang datin Umairah), Hani dan kalsom berbincang, Datin Umairah menerangkan usaha yang dibuatnya sehingga dapat tahu status Hani. Sebaliknya bapa Shariff menyarankan selidiki lagi. Hani merayu dan berharap jangan sama sekali anggapkan dia ingin mengambil kesempatan.

Mungkin Tengku Zaharah akan berubah.Zalia pegang kata kata Zahid.Tengku Zarif cuba untuk menenangkan Zalia dan tidak mahu dia terlalu bersedih kerana akan mengganggu emosi anak yang bakal lahir dia hanya mahu menggembirakan Zalia.

programme.title: Anda Telah Di Prank
programme.desc: ADAM dan SURIA adalah sepasang kekasih yang memang sehati sejiwa. Hobi mereka ialah, mengenakan orang bersama dua lagi kawan, Johan dan Kamil. Suatu hari, Suria menghubungi Nia, kawannya melalui panggilan video. Nia terkejut apabila melihat ada seseorang dalam rumah Suria. Keadaan menjadi cemas dan tak terkawal apabila seseorang itu membunuh Suria dan memberitahu dia akan datang mencari Nia pula. Nia yang cemas terus berlari mengambil pisau. Malangnya, pisau itu tertikam dirinya sendiri. Semasa Nia bergelut dengan kematian, Suria,Adam, Johan dan Kamil ketawa dan menjerit, Anda telah diprank! Kematian Nia menyebabkan Suria dan Adam rasa bersalah. Ia juga menjadi tajuk utama berita. Adam, Suria, Johan dan Kamil turut ditahan untuk membantu siasatan namun kematian Nia diklasifikasikan sebagai kemalangan dan mereka dibebaskan. Malangnya tidak lama selepas kematian Nia, Johan dan Kamil telah dibunuh! Kemudian, seorang demi seorang yang membuat prank lain, akan dibunuh oleh seseorang berhoodie yang mengatakan, Anda telah diprank! sebelum membunuh mereka. Kejadian ini menggemparkan negara dan membuatkan Adam, terutamanya Suria hidup dalam ketakutan. Suria dan Adam cuba menyiasat dalam usaha menyelamatkan diri mereka dari ketakutan dibunuh. Mereka percaya hantu Nia adalah seseorang yang ingin membalas dendam. Apabila segalanya terbongkar, seseorang berhoodie itu sebenarnya adalah Mimie, childhood friend Nia yang rupa-rupanya menyaksikan kematian Nia pada malam prank itu. Dia sangat membenci budaya prank dan bertekad untuk membalas dendam demi menghapuskan manusia tak guna ini dari muka bumi.

programme.title: Foreigner
programme.desc: Kisah ahli perniagaan London yang rendah hati Quan (Chan), yang masa lalunya yang telah lama terkubur meletus dalam dendam yang didorong oleh dendam apabila satu-satunya orang yang ditinggalkan untuk dicintainya - anak perempuan remajanya - diambil daripadanya dalam tindakan keganasan bermotif politik yang tidak masuk akal . Dalam pencarian tanpa henti untuk identiti pengganas, Quan terpaksa terlibat dalam konflik kucing-dan-tikus dengan seorang pegawai kerajaan Ireland (Brosnan), yang masa lalunya mungkin mengandungi petunjuk tentang identiti pembunuh yang sukar difahami.

programme.title: 3AM Ep 4 Ep4
programme.desc: Sekumpulan kawan pergi berkhemah di dalam hutan yang kononnya berhantu walaupun memberi amaran untuk tidak berbuat demikian. Apabila malam tiba dan perkhemahan ditetapkan, hubungan nafsu dan cinta yang rumit antara mereka terdedah, mencetuskan satu siri peristiwa paranormal yang menghukum mereka. Apabila fajar menyingsing, siapa yang akan keluar dari hutan hidup-hidup?

programme.title: UC 2

programme.title: The Cave
programme.desc: Apabila pasukan bola sepak remaja yang terdiri daripada 12 lelaki, berumur 11-16, dan jurulatih mereka berusia 25 tahun terperangkap jauh di dalam gua di Utara Thailand, beribu-ribu sukarelawan dan tentera dari seluruh dunia bersatu dalam perlumbaan melawan masa untuk mencari mereka . Sebaik sahaja kanak-kanak lelaki itu ditemui hidup sepuluh hari kemudian, satu-satunya jalan keluar ialah berenang selama lima jam yang mustahil yang hanya penyelam gua yang pakar boleh bertahan. Di Ireland, juruelektrik kilang kapal terbang dan penyelam gua rekreasi Jim Warny menerima panggilan: "Berapa lama lagi anda boleh berada di sini?" Tiba di Thailand, Jim melangkah keluar dari pesawat dan masuk ke dalam gua - misi tiga hari bermata pisau sedang dijalankan. Berdasarkan peristiwa sebenar, THE CAVE menceritakan kisah mendebarkan tentang misi menyelamat antarabangsa terbesar pada zaman moden, dari perspektif unik lelaki dan wanita yang menghadapi keputusan hidup dan mati dan mempamerkan keazaman dan pengorbanan yang tidak mementingkan diri sendiri, yang memuncak dengan keputusan yang berjaya menentang semua kemungkinan.

programme.title: UC 5
programme.desc: Salih ditembak dengan senapang di hutan tempat dia pergi berburu bersama rakannya Metin. Salih, yang terpaksa hidup dengan peluru di otaknya, memerlukan bantuan material dan rohani untuk sembuh. Metin, yang mengatakan bahawa dia akan melakukan semua jenis bantuan kepada Salih pada mulanya. Kemudian bertunang dengan teman wanita Salih iaitu Sermin, meninggalkan Salih dengan ibunya sendirian. Arzu, bekas tunang Metin, tidak dapat memahami apa yang berlaku. Semasa cuba mencari tahu mengapa Metin berkelakuan sedemikian, Salih dan ibunya, seorang wanita luar biasa, melawat Trkan.

programme.title: Kampung Drift
programme.desc: Mengisahkan pengembaraan hidup seorang remaja bernama Johan dalam mencari erti kejayaan dan kehidupan menerusi sukan drift yang berkait rapat dengan sejarah hidupnya. Walaupun ditentang keras oleh ayahnya untuk menyertai sukan drift, minat Johan terhadap sukan itu tidak pernah pudar. Bersama-sama kawan baiknya, Bojeng, pakciknya, Ajoi, dan saintis gila, Pak Idon, dia akan menggunakan apa sahaja cara untuk melibatkan diri secara aktif dalam sukan pemotoran drift itu. Minat Johan mula bertukar menjadi sebuah impian besar apabila dia mendapat tahu sejarah hitam ayahnya yang berkait rapat dengan sukan drift. Namun, penglibatan Johan dalam sukan drift ini menghadapi jalan sukar apabila dia terlibat dalam pelbagai konflik diri, masalah cinta dan persaingan di antara Julia, Shiela dan Ray, drifter ternama dari Kuala Lumpur. Semua ini pula bakal membawa kepada kematian orang yang disayanginya. Johan cuba mengubah sejarah dengan menggunakan mesin merentas masa untuk kembali ke masa silam. Berjayakah dia? Semuanya bakal terjawab dalam Kampung Drift.

Sarakit pula tidak berbau apa-apa dan menjelaskan duit itu simpanannya. Rafiq juga mulai nampak bayangan kayu dan cacing pada lauk ayam yang dimasak Sarakit. Setelah kematian Tat, Jali sekarang menjadi sasaran hantu tenggek dan sering diganggu. Mariam pula dimarahi abangnya kerana menggunakan bomoh untuk memisahkan Sarakit dari Rafiq dan memintanya menarik balik segala yang dilakukan. Mariam tidak mengendahkan nasihat abangnya dan dia juga sering diganggu bayangan Sarakit.

programme.title: The Invoking 5

programme.desc: Adruce, seorang budak yang kuat berangan dan sering tidur dalam kelas. Pada suatu hari, Adruce membawa pulang sebuah alat berbentuk topi yang dijumpainya di dalam semak. programme.title: Ular
programme.desc: Myra ialah seorang wartawan jenayah yang digantung kerja telah diarahkan untuk membuat liputan di sebuah pusat peranginan di sebuah pulau. Dia yang ditemani jurukameranya, Remy tidak pernah menyangka tugasannya kali ini bukanlah satu tugasan biasa apabila percutian hebat yang dimenangi oleh 10 orang pemenang cabutan bertuah bertukar menjadi sebuah mimpi ngeri. Segalanya bermula apabila ada di antara tetamu pusat peranginan itu dengan beraninya telah menyelinap masuk ke dalam hutan yang telah dipagari dengan pagar elektrik. Rambo yang panik setelah menyedari hal tersebut segera mendapatkan Encik Aziz, pemilik pusat peranginan tersebut. Ia secara tidak langsung telah menimbulkan rasa ingin tahu Myra dan Remy untuk merungkai apakah rahsia yang cuba disembunyikan oleh Encik Aziz di sebalik kewujudan pusat peranginan tersebut.

programme.title: Magika
programme.desc: Mengisahkan dua beradik, Ayu dan Malik yang tersesat di alam bunian selepas keluar rumah pada waktu maghrib. programme.title: Puaka Balai Gombak
programme.desc: Sekumpulan anak muda yang menggelarkan diri mereka Puaka X gemar pergi ke beberapa tempat yang dikatakan berhantu. Mereka menggunakan pendekatan berbeza daripada kumpulan paranormal yang lain. Semakin hari, Puaka X semakin galak mencabar sesiapa di luar sana untuk membuktikan kewujudan hantu. Pada suatu hari mereka menerima cabaran daripada seseorang yang tidak dikenali untuk pergi ke lokasi bernama Balai Gombak. Tanpa disedari, ada sesuatu yang menanti mereka di sana.

programme.title: Pontianak Menjerit
programme.desc: Selepas kematian Datuk Pangeran Abdul Rahman, waris-warisnya dipanggil untuk mendengar wasiat yang ditulisnya. Harta peninggalannya sebanyak RM30 juta akan dibahagikan kepada Azlee, Mazlan, Saiful serta isteri mudanya, Ratana Putri, seorang wanita Thailand. Azlee tidak puas hati sebab tak mahu berkongsi harta dengan pewaris lain. Lalu berlakulah pertengkaran kecil antara Azlee, Saiful dan Ratana Puri. Peguam arwah Datuk Pangeran menjelaskan terdapat syarat untuk memiliki harta tersebut, iaitu kesemua waris-waris diminta untuk menetap di banglo besar itu selama 33 hari. Dalam ketegangan yangg berlaku diantara Azlee, Saiful dan Ratana Putri, tiba-tiba mereka dikejutkan dengan kehadiran pontianak di banglo tersebut.

programme.title: Anak Niat
programme.desc: Juita dipanggil anak niat yang ditatah penuh kasih sayang oleh ibu dan bapanya, Orang Kaya dan Faridah. Ibu dan bapa Juita bernazar kepada Keramat untuk mendapatkan seorang anak iaitu Juita namun tidak mahu menerima kenyataan bahawa perbuatan itu adalah syirik. Juita kemudian menjalinkan hubungan bersama Jidot. Abang Mat pula sedih kerana sering dipandang hina oleh Orang Kaya dan Juita hanya kerana dia seorang pembantu yang diupah oleh mereka. Kebenaran terbongkar apabila Abang Mat ialah bapa kepada Jidot dan juga Juita.

programme.title: Perjanjian Syaitan
programme.desc: Tambun membunuh Tok Kadim, penghulu di sebuah kampung dan kemudiannya mengatakan bahawa Tok Kadim mati satu kemalangan. Selepas kejadian itu, Tambun dilantik menjadi ketua kampung yang baharu. Pada masa yang sama, Ribut, adik kepada Tambun yang berwajah hodoh ingin membalas dendam kepada Ujang kerana menolak cintanya dan memilih Seri sebagai teman. Ribut bersahabat dengan syaitan yang berjanji untuk menjadikannya seorang perempuan cantik. Sejak itulah Ribut berusaha untuk membalas dendam sehingga berlaku beberapa siri kematian yang penuh misteri.

programme.title: Jin Notti
programme.desc: Segala yang berlaku dalam dunia jin akan bertentangan dengan alam manusia. Notti, seekor anak jin dihukum kerana sering membuat keburukan dalam dunianya. Hukuman yang dijatuhkan kepadanya ialah dia perlu turun ke bumi dan untuk bergaul dengan orang-orang jahat. Ketika berada di bumi, Notti perlu masuk ke dalam tubuh manusia dan membuat kejahatan namun dia sering gagal. Lebih merumitkan keadaan, Notti mula jatuh cinta dengan seorang lelaki bernama Aziz.

programme.title: 2 Alam
programme.desc: Amy(Adam) melanjutkan pengajiannya di London. Semasa berada di sana, dia terpengaruh dengan budaya barat. Dia sanggup membuat pembedahan menukar jantina dan berkahwin dengan seorang lelaki Inggeris. Sekian lama membuat dosa, Amy(Adam) akhirnya nekad untuk mengambil nyawanya sendiri. Perjalanan terakhir Adam menuju liang lahad menjadi sukar dengan kejadian pelbagai peristiwa aneh.

programme.title: Duhai Si Pari Pari
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Syadon, seorang pemuda yang mencintai Mala. Pada suatu hari, Syadon bertemu seorang gadis bernama Pari yang sedang mencari kekasihnya. Semakin hari, Pari semakin suntuk waktu yang Pari ada untuk mengahwini jejaka idamannya dan pulang ke dunia kayangan. Syadon bertanya siapakah Pari yang sebenarnya dan setelah diterangkan, dia sukar mempercayainya. Pari terpaksa membuktikan kata-katanya dengan menunaikan permintaan Syadon.

programme.title: Seru
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang sebuah produksi yang sedang membuat satu penggambaran filem seram bertajuk "Jangan Bernafas". Semasa penggambaran berlangsung, secara tiba-tiba, pelbagai kejadian aneh dan peristiwa berlaku, diluar jangkaan mereka. Pada mulanya, mereka menganggap ia hanyalah rasukan biasa dan kru di sebalik pembikinan filem tersebut, ingin menjadikannya sebagai "footage" menarik untuk tujuan promosi filem tersebut. Namun, seorang demi seorang menjadi sasaran rasukan dan juga pembunuhan, menyebabkan keadaan menjadi tidak terkawal... tetapi kamera yang digunakan, masih terus merakamkan aksi yang terjadi.

Dengan perasaan kecewa dia membawa diri pulang ke kampung dan di sana lebih banyak waktunya diisi dengan menonton filem hebat. Namun aktiviti hariannya itu tidak disenangi emaknya, Cik Leha, seorang penjual jamu yang berjaya di kampung itu.

programme.title: Mv Seleksi Sinema Ep3
programme.desc: Seleksi lagu-lagu menarik untuk hiburan anda

programme.title: Bonchu 7
programme.desc: Boonchu dan Molee akan berkahwin. Tetapi mereka berdua mempunyai tugas khas yang perlu diselesaikan untuk membuktikan cinta sejati mereka kepada Manee, kakak Molee.

programme.title: Pening-Pening Lalat
programme.desc: Dino adalah banduan yang berjaya melarikan diri dari penjara. Polis menyiarkan berita mengenainya dan menawarkan hadiah RM10,000 kepada sesiapa yang berjaya menangkapnya. Jadi Dino bersembunyi di dalam hutan di mana dia bertemu Zakaria dan Aliza.

programme.title: Istri Yang Tidak Benar-Benar Dicintai Oleh Suaminya
programme.desc: Selepas kemalangan kereta itu, Citra menjadi buta. Dia dianggap tidak mampu melayani suaminya Johan, dan ibu mertuanya menekan Johan untuk berkahwin dengan Priska. Akankah Citra mampu bertahan atau akan berpisah dengan Johan?

programme.title: D'Academy 5 Ep75
programme.desc: D'Academy kini kembali! D'Academy atau DA (singkatan dari Dangdut Academy) ialah pertunjukan bakat muzik dangdut yang pertama dan terbesar. Acara ini telah berjaya membangkitkan fenomena muzik dangdut, dan program ini telah menjadi salah satu pertunjukan pencarian bakat yang paling berjaya di Indonesia. Musim ini merupakan musim kelima dan diadakan buat kali pertama selepas tidak dihadirkan selama lima tahun.

programme.title: Inbox 2022 Ep6
programme.desc: Rancangan varia muzik yang mengandungi muzik, permainan dan aktiviti yang menyeronokkan.

programme.title: Tamu Idola Ep3
programme.desc: Sebuah rancangan realiti yang mengejutkan di mana artis memasuki dunia peminat mereka, dengan mengunjungi mereka secara tiba-tiba. Penonton dapat melihat momen intim ketika artis terlibat dalam rutinitas rutin harian dan pengalaman para peminat setia mereka.

programme.title: Cinta Setelah Cinta Ep91
programme.desc: Starla dan Niko merupakan pasangan yang sempurna. Mereka mempunyai dua orang anak, iaitu Nila dan Daffa. Walaupun begitu, Niko secara rahsia menjalinkan hubungan dengan Ayu, rakan lama Starla dan Niko dari sekolah menengah. Mereka berdua cuba menyembunyikan hubungan tersebut dari siapa pun. Suatu hari, Ilham, suami Ayu, melihat mereka bermesraan di dalam kereta. Niko dan Ayu melarikan diri, Ilham mengejar mereka. Malangnya, mereka bertiga akhirnya terlibat dalam kemalangan.

programme.title: Anak Penjual Ikan Asin Sukses Jadi Pengusaha Kapal
programme.desc: Kehilangan bapanya pada usia muda, Arief terpaksa membantu ibunya menjual ikan masin untuk mencari nafkah. Perjuangan Arief berbuah hasil, kerana di masa depan beliau berjaya menjadi usahawan kapal yang berjaya seperti arwah ayahnya.

programme.title: Tajwid Cinta Ep181
programme.desc: Dafri baru saja kembali ke Indonesia untuk bertemu dengan Alina dan bertunang. Walau bagaimanapun, pertunangan itu terhalang kerana Nadia tidak suka dengan hubungan Dafri Bersama anak perempuannya, Alina. Nadia dengan sengaja menghantar Dafri untuk belajar di Turki agar Dafri jauh dari anak perempuannya. Selain itu, ayah Dafri meminta Dafri untuk berkahwin dengan Syifa, seorang wanita yang pertama kali Dafri temui. Pada ketika itu, Syifa gagal berkahwin kerana bakal suaminya, Ilham, tiba-tiba menghilangkan diri. Selepas berkahwin dengan Dafri, Syifa dan suaminya tinggal di Jakarta.

Sebagai seorang istri dan ibu, Meli sangatlah terluka dan kecewa apabila ia dikhianati oleh suaminya. Arga seolah-olah hanya menggunakan Meli sebagai alat untuk memperoleh wang sementara dia sendiri menikah dengan pengasuh anaknya. Meli juga harus berjuang untuk memenangi semula kasih sayang anaknya yang telah dipaksa membencinya oleh Arga dan Ayu. Apakah yang sebenarnya berlaku?

programme.title: Janji Palsu Suamiku, Derita Buatku
programme.desc: Tomy melamar Alda dan menjanjikan akan merawat kebutuhan ibu dan adik calon istrinya. Setelah pernikahan, usaha Tomy mengalami penurunan dan ibunya menyalahkan Alda karena miskin dan tidak bisa membantu suaminya. Ketika usahanya mulai membaik, Tomy berselingkuh dengan mitra bisnisnya. Akankah Alda mampu menerima kenyataan ini?

programme.title: The Closet
programme.desc: After losing his wife, a father tries to start over in a new home with his daughter. But things take a turn when strange noises trickle out of the closet, and his daughter goes missing.

programme.title: Juror 8
programme.desc: Based on a true story, eight ordinary people of different backgrounds were selected as the first jury for a murder trial in South Korea in 2008.

programme.title: Hot Blooded
programme.desc: A small and quiet port in Busan outskirt became the battlefield of local gangsters.

programme.title: Samjin Company English Class
programme.desc: In the mid-1990s in South Korea, three female office co-workers who enroll in English classes in hopes to advance their careers, struggle to expose the corruption inside their company.

programme.title: I Am The King
programme.desc: A runaway prince meets a slave who bears a strikingly similar appearance to himself. The prince gets mistaken as the slave and the slave is crowned as King.

programme.title: Decibel
programme.desc: A former navy commander receives a threatening call who claims to blow up a stadium with a sound-responsive bomb. He must face the secret he left buried in the deep sea to track this terrorist down.

programme.title: Door Lock
programme.desc: A woman, living by herself, finds her door lock cover left open one day. Startled by this, she starts investigating on her own and finds more hints of someone trying to enter her home.

programme.title: Perfect Game
programme.desc: On May 16, 1987, Korea's two greatest pitchers of the day, face off to determine who is the better pitcher, in an epic game that would go down in baseball history.

programme.title: Cadaver
programme.desc: 6 med students participate in their first anatomy class, yet nightmare begins when they are assigned with a deadly beautiful cadaver.

programme.title: The Tenor - Lirico Spinto
programme.desc: A strong partnership and friendship begins when a talented Korean vocalist met a Japanese music producer. At the peak of his career, he was diagnosed with thyroid cancer and might loss his voice...

programme.title: Mission: Possible
programme.desc: A cash-strapped private investigator Woo Su-Han is retained by a secret agent Yoo Da-Hee to bring down a high risk arms trafficking operation.

programme.title: 1987: When The Day Comes
programme.desc: In 1987, a pro-democracy student activist was captured and tortured to death by the police. The authorities tried to cover up the case, but the ordinary people fight to reveal the truth.

programme.title: The Roundup
programme.desc: 4 years after the events of Garibong district round up operation, Geumcheon Polices Major Crimes Unit is given a mission to repatriate a fugitive who fled to Vietnam.

programme.title: I (2021)
programme.desc: Ah-Young who grew up in an orphanage becomes the babysitter of Young-Chae, who is raising a 6-month-old child on her own. One day, her child has an accident and she places all the blame on Ah-Young...

programme.title: The Tiger
programme.desc: While the Kingdom of Korea is under occupation by the Japanese, an old and experienced hunter is challenged by the hunt of the last tiger in the country.

programme.title: My Lovely Angel
programme.desc: A man bears the responsibility to take care of a deaf-blind girl unexpectedly, which turns out to be life-changing to both of them.

programme.title: Ashfall
programme.desc: When a volcano straddling the ChinaNorth Korea border erupts, earthquakes ensue causing pandemonium in both North and South Korea.

programme.title: Race To Freedom: Um Bok Dong

programme.title: Blessing of Formosa (T) Ep211
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

Although Siou-Ying was betrayed by You-Tsai, she has still been a dutiful daughter to her mother-in-law, and has single-mindedly raised four children.

programme.title: Player In Kaohsiung (M) Ep60
programme.desc: The name Kaohsiung has entered into a century of history since it has been renamed from Da Gou. This year, the National Day fireworks will be held again in Kaohsiung after 20 years passed. SETI has specially produced a new travelogue for Kaohsiung, leading the audience to visit the most popular, charming, and unique places in Kaohsiung. Through the lens, the century-old glory of Kaohsiungs [One-Hundred] is presented profoundly. The new season of "Player in Kaohsiung" invites many hosts and celebrities, including Yao Yao, Chang Chin Lan, Daniel Chen, David Wu, Ada Chang, Fay Wu, and Kua Kua, visit the 38 administrative districts of Kaohsiung to explore the sensational stories of the people in the alleys, deeply explore the professional spirit of the Greater Kaohsiung area, the traditions and customs of the aboriginal people, the living beside the farms and ports, and the humanism nurtured by Kaohsiungs century-old history.

programme.title: Walker Fun Kaohsiung (M) Ep211
programme.desc: Walker Fun Kaohsiung is a travel reality show that takes viewers on an exciting journey through the vibrant city of Kaohsiung. With 35 different routes, the show explores the citys hidden gems, local culture, and unique experiences. From bustling night markets to serene temples, Walker Fun Kaohsiung showcases the best of Kaohsiung.

programme.title: Have A Nice Dream (M) Ep14
programme.desc: Five young professionals with different life skills, team up for two days and one night trip, leading the audiance to explore the good life of nature and the beauty of the land of Taiwan.

programme.title: Way to Health (M) Ep295296
programme.desc: This show invites top medical professionals from different fields to answer questions from the audience. Approved by the medical world, this show is an influential, as well as reliable place to understand more about ones health.

programme.title: Mr.Player (M) Ep502
programme.desc: Depending on the locations of the missions, Jacky Wu, the leader of the home team, invites various celebrities to take on challenges and bring you excitement every week.

programme.title: My Hero, My Daddy (M) Ep2223
programme.desc: A fathers love for his daughters landed Jinfa Huang in battles against other men right within his family, as he found himself in conflict with his sons-in-law. His 3 daughters each possessed a distinct personality but were similarly headstrong and in romantic relationships that caused their fathers brows to crease. Tianlan, his eldest, was in love with Minglu Xu, Jinfas superior who never missed an opportunity to make life difficult for him; Tianhong, his second daughter, was drifting apart from him because of her husband; meanwhile, his youngest girl was challenging the taboo of a campus romance. How would Jinfa emerge victor in this fight to protect the 3 loves of his life?

programme.title: Trivisa
programme.desc: In the beginning of 1997, Hong Kong's three notorious thieves who have never met one another before appear in the same restaurant. This leads to a rumour that they are joining forces to pull off something big before the Handover, though this is not something that any of them is aware of.

programme.title: Princess and 7 Kung Fu Masters
programme.desc: Seven Kung Fu masters live in Lucky Town, the only safe residing place in northeast China. When warlord Lam refuses to side with the Japanese, an agent is assigned to take over his army and kill his daughter using ninjutsu. Lams daughter escapes and seeks help from the seven masters, who finally defeat the enemy and save the warlord!

programme.title: May We Chat
programme.desc: Yan, Wei Wei and Yi Ji are three troubled young women from very different backgrounds who met on We Chat, a social media platform, and will do anything to escape each of their troubled lives. When Yan suddenly disappears one day, Wei Wei and Yi Ji start to track her whereabouts, only to find out shocking truths about her that were never revealed.

programme.title: The Rescue
programme.desc: An emergency occurs on an offshore drilling rig that would cause it to capsize and sink. The Emergency Response Unit races against the clock in a chopper rescue mission amidst dangerous explosions and fire. Captain Gao Qian must work seamlessly with his chopper pilot Zhao Cheng to rescue survivors using the most maverick and dangerous tactics.

programme.title: See You Tomorrow
programme.desc: In this chaotic world, every city has its own "navigators" who can help solve various relationship issues. Bar owner Chen and his partner Guan are legendary navigators, but in the process of helping a girl Xiao Yu, they must also face their own problems in an epic act of self-discovery that brings their lives from towering highs to withering lows.

programme.title: The Comeback
programme.desc: Uncle Hua is a retired agent who owns an antique shop on an old street. When the old street is forcibly demolished by the local Green Dragon Gang one day, Uncle Huas hidden identity is accidentally revealed, and he is pursued by a mysterious organization headed by Ah Jie. A fatal duel has just begun!

programme.title: My Kung Fu Sweetheart
programme.desc: Phoenixs (Cecilia Cheung) parents are martial arts superheroes, who hide their true identities while ferreting out evil martial artists. Phoenix gets the go-ahead to train in the misty mountains, where she learns of her all-important romantic destiny...

programme.title: Flying Dragon Leaping Tiger
programme.desc: Lu the horse thief is betrayed by his best mate Qiao and is separated from his son. Lus wife blames him for it and takes Qiaos daughter away as revenge. For 20 years, Lu searches for his wife until one day, his missing son meets Qiaos daughter and they fall in love. Will their hatred pass on to the next generation?

programme.title: My Prince Edward
programme.desc: A newly engaged Hong Kong woman tries to rid herself of a secret sham marriage to a mainlander that she was paid for years ago, before she can get married for real. Winner of Best Original Film Score and Best New Director at the 39th Hong Kong Film Awards.

programme.title: Everything is Unknown
programme.desc: Pan Yi Ming receives his father's will stating that he must attend his funeral at home to claim the huge inheritance. When he returns home, he encounters his ex-girlfriend, her husband Hua Qi and his daughter whom he has never met. When Pan discovers that his daughter is being abused by Hua, he vows to save her but eventually fall into their trap

programme.title: The Knight of Shadows: Between Yin and Yang
programme.desc: Pu Song Ling, a legendary demon hunter, is asked to investigate a case involving missing teenage village girls with disciple, Constable Yan Fei. The duo leads a group of little monsters to help with the investigation, and in their search for the truth, they accidentally discover a mysterious love between a knight and a female ghost.

programme.title: The White Storm 2: Drug Lords
programme.desc: In this epic action-thriller starring Andy Lau and Louis Koo, the two award-winning best actors star on opposing sides of a drug war. As a bounty of $100 million Hong Kong dollars is made to hunt down the biggest drug dealer in the city, Hong Kong becomes the battleground for the fight between good and evil.

programme.title: Ready O/R Knot
programme.desc: Guy and Heidi have been together for five years since they first met in a wedding banquet, but marriage soon becomes a challenge to their relationship. Heidi sees marriage as a testimony of their love, while Guy sees it as doomsday. Can the couple resolve their conflict? Are they ready or not?

programme.title: Moscow Mission
programme.desc: Based on the 1993 true event of the "China-Russia Train Robbery", a gang of criminals commits a heist, stealing cash and goods from the cross border train. A Chinese police officer disguises as a businessman takes charge of the operation to arrest the criminals, but uncovers a bigger conspiracy instead

programme.title: Still Human
programme.desc: Evelyn, a Filipino domestic helper, moves to Hong Kong to work for Cheong Wing, a divorcee paralyzed in a construction accident. Becoming unlikely friends, the two discover shared humanity that helps them face lifes mounting hardships.

programme.title: The Monkey King 2
programme.desc: Monkey King is tasked with escorting Monk Tang on his journey to the West to retrieve the scriptures. During the trip, Monk Tang is being targeted by the seductive yet deadly White Bone Spirit, who feeds on the innocents to gain immortality. Monkey King will have to fight the White Bone Spirit in order to save Monk Tang!

programme.title: I Believe
programme.desc: Chu Chu has been waiting for her first love for 10 years but he marries someone else in the end. As she loses faith in love, she meets a wedding planner and a handsome and rich man, who both help her get over her ex-boyfriend. As Chu Chu feels the same love from them, she must make up her mind. Who will she choose in the end?

programme.title: Distinction
programme.desc: A music teacher in a special needs school, an underachiever from an elite school, and a rebellious teenager with a handicapped brother take part in a campus musical for various reasons. Little did they know that this turns out to be a journey of self-discovery.

programme.title: Enter the Fat Dragon
programme.desc: Donnie Yen plays a Hong Kong police officer who is highly skilled in martial arts but balloons to more than 200 pounds after his fianc left him. His boss can only assign simple tasks to him like escorting a criminal to Japan, but can he complete it?

programme.title: Trending Topic
programme.desc: Chen Miao, an online media editor-in-chief, wrote a popular article which has become a trending topic. This however, led indirectly to a girls suicide. After receiving a help request, she realises that there is more to the story than meets the eye. As public opinion sways on the case, a war to speak up for the weak has begun!

programme.title: Ip Man 3
programme.desc: When some gangsters led by a ruthless American property developer force a school to sell their land, Ip Man fights to protect it. Subsequently, Ip Man is challenged by another Wing Chun master Zhang Tian Zhi for the Grandmaster title. Ip Man accepts the challenge for the sake of his family and disciples, and wins the duel for the title.

programme.title: Hero Among Heroes
programme.desc: Wong Fei Hung assists Lin Ze Xu to crack down the opium trading in Guangzhou. Barac provokes Beggar So to kill Wong and Lin as they hinder his opium business. When So finally resolves his misunderstanding with Wong, he decides to join Wong to defeat Barac and stop the opium import.

programme.title: The Silent War
programme.desc: After the Chinese Civil War, 701 Bureau continues to monitor the coded transmissions between rebel forces. When radio frequencies used by the opponent disappear suddenly, Agent Zhang asks Ho, a blind piano tuner with exceptional hearing, to help find the transmission signals. Can Ho find the missing signals and foil a possible assassination plot?

programme.title: Wise Guys Never Die
programme.desc: Nick meets Teddy, a con artiste, when he is sent to prison for embezzlement, and Teddy teaches him all the gambling tricks. After their release, they team up with Teddys lover Lora, to take revenge on Dragon, who framed Teddy for his sentence. Nick though is seduced by Lora and they end up in an affair. Will Nick finally join Teddy in his revenge?

programme.title: Endgame
programme.desc: A killer and a stage actor accidentally swapped their identities at a bathhouse. The actor must complete the killers mission while the killer thinks he is a hopeless actor after losing his memory during the accident. When the killer strives to become a successful stage actor, he also starts to recall what has happened

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 1
programme.desc: Wu Dang Sects Zhang Chui Shans son, Zhang Wu Ji, finds himself accidentally embroiled in the fight for the Dragon Sabre. When he unwittingly learns the powerful martial arts skills from the Jiuyin scriptures, Wu Ji proceeds to help the Six Major sects fight against the corrupt government.

programme.title: Caught in Time
programme.desc: Based on true events, Detective Zhong Cheng leads a task force in pursuit of Eagle, a criminal gang led by Zhang Sun. Highly methodical and disciplined, the gang manages to avoid capture after each heist. A decade later, the need to stop Eagle is more urgent than ever when Zhong Cheng realizes that his time is almost up to solve the case.

programme.title: Tales from the Occult: Ultimate Malevolence
programme.desc: The final chapter of 'Tales From The Occult', the movie features three short stories about two high school friends, a magician undergoing hypnosis to find her missing friend, and a man finding his way out of a mysterious building. The stories reveal the most terrifying and ugly side of human nature, where life and death are just a thought away!

programme.title: Fight Back to School
programme.desc: The number one killer in SDU, Chow Sing Sing(Stephen Chow), is sent to a school to find a lost gun. His partner Tat(Ng Man Tat) pretends to be a school worker in assisting him. They recognize that some students are being closed with Fei, the head of triad society, and Fei traffics munitions. Sing steals and ignites Fei's munitions; Fei pledges to kill Sing...

programme.title: Detective Vs. Sleuths
programme.desc: Hong Kong is rocked by a series of cold-blooded murders whose victims are runaway suspects of unsolved cases. The group of killers calls themselves The Chosen Sleuths". Former top detective Lee vows to bring the brutal killers to justice and prove himself to be the real Chosen Sleuth instead of a lunatic.

programme.title: The Brotherhood of Rebel
programme.desc: Chai, a triad member, helps his childhood friend Meow flee Hong Kong after discovering that Meow attempted to kill his triad boss. 17 years later, Chai becomes a key member of the triad. When he runs into Meow one day, he knows that his gang will kill Meow if they find him. Caught between triad and brotherhood, what will Chai choose?

programme.title: Tainted Love
programme.desc: Office lady Zhou Ran falls victim to an online dating love scam and is cheated of 550,000 yuan. Following faint clues left by the scammer, Zhou Ran comes to a small coastal town and encounters two young men. She gradually discovers that these two men have hidden the clues of the scam, and sets out on her revenge plan.

programme.title: Europe Raiders
programme.desc: Mr Lin and Miss Wang are the two top bounty hunters in the business, and are searching for the destructive missile Hand of God to prove who is the better bounty hunter. They soon realize they are not the only ones after the missile. Will Lin and Wang put their differences aside and work together in search for the Hand of God?

programme.title: Executioners From Shaolin
programme.desc: The White-Browed Priest supports the brutal Qing government, burning down Shaolin Temple and hunting its disciples. Hung from Shaolin falls in love with Fang while escaping from the hunt and the couple have a son before Hung is killed by the Priest. To avenge his father, Hung creates a new form of martial art combining his parents kung fu styles.

programme.title: A Friend from Inner Space
programme.desc: A young boy whose parents are separated tries to find happiness in life. One day, he meets and befriends a kind-hearted spirit Ren, who decides to make him truly happy by getting his parents back together.

programme.title: Judgement of an Assassin
programme.desc: An evil clan plans a discord so as to dominate the martial arts world. Their masked assassins massacre another clan and one of the assassins is arrested and brought to trial at a tribunal of all the clans. What judgement will they make and can they uncover the truth?

programme.title: Hong Kong 73
programme.desc: In 1973, the Hong Kong Heng Seng Index hit extraordinary peaks and people from all walks of life go stock market crazy. Meanwhile, Hong Kong's social problems build up without anyone paying attention to what are actually happening to the crazy lives of people, in this mad city that many call home...

programme.title: Trilogy Of Swordsmanship
programme.desc: A kung fu anthology film consisting of three stories: a man embarrasses himself while trying to prove his worth to the father of the woman he loves; a courtesan in love with a general will need to deliver a notorious bandit in exchange for him not being executed; and a group of bandits forms a plan to rescue a new friend from being executed.

programme.title: Crazy Shaolin Disciples
programme.desc: Three young kung-fu warriors from wildly different backgrounds become students of Shaolin at the same temple. These three warriors are: Royal Guard Lo Lieh, fleeing soldier, Lo Meng, and villager, Wang Yu.

programme.title: All Men are Brothers
programme.desc: This is a sequel to Chang Chehs epic The Water Margin, and follows the patriotic story of seven warriors in the band of 108 outlaws at Mount Liang. The magnificent seven battle against the despotic government officials to save their country.

programme.title: The Emperor and the Minister
programme.desc: The ingenious imperial scholar Liu Yung always embarrasses Emperor Chien Lung with his quick wit and gift of gab. The emperor purposely sets him up to solve the seemingly unsolvable. However, Liu Yung resolves it easily with wit and style and foils the emperors plot once again.

programme.title: The Master
programme.desc: Gao Jian is the disciple of the martial arts master Shi but is constantly being punished by his master for no reason. One day, Gao accidentally saves his masters rival Jin, so Jin teaches him his unique martial arts skill in return. However, Master Shi sees this as Gaos betrayal

programme.title: Rose, Be My Love
programme.desc: Not a love triangle but a love 'rectangle', Rose, Be My Love is a romantic drama set on the eve of World War II that represents the high standards achieved by Shaw Brothers in both aspects of star power and technical polish.

programme.title: Black Magic 2
programme.desc: Doctor Sing is puzzled by the strange symptoms of his patients and asks his friend for help. The sickness is apparently caused by a black magic that is casted by a wicked man Kong. Kong covets the beauty of Sings wife and casts an evil love spell on her, while threatening to kill Sing at the same time. Can Sing save his wife and his patients?

programme.title: The Eunuch
programme.desc: A year before Lo Wei directed Bruce Lee in Fist Of Fury, he wrote and co-starred in this tale of a treacherous devil who wants nothing less than supreme power...and doesn't care if he has to murder the Emperor and use his own daughter as a deadly dupe to get it.

programme.title: Pursuit of Vengeance
programme.desc: Kung Fu legend Ti Lung stars in the action movie as Fu Xue Hong, embarking on a epic journey of revenge for his father.

programme.title: We Love Millionaires
programme.desc: In this romantic comedy, three beautiful Hong Kong salesgirls travel to Osaka in Japan to pursue their dreams of marrying a rich man. They masquerade as high society debutantes and make their way to a posh resort to meet and woo millionaires (or fake ones!).

programme.title: Notorious Eight
programme.desc: The young Chen Chi-chin (Liu Yung) loses heavily to experienced gambler Hu Kuan-ten (Lo Lieh). His father loses at cards and dies of shock. Chen appeals to his uncle who summons seven fellow professional gamblers to carry out vengeance. Much more than a gambling film, this is a thrilling melting pot of martial arts stars, extortion, illicit love, poker-face vengeance, and all sorts of edge-of-your-seat gambling duels. Featuring two of the leading action stars of the era, Chen Kuen-tai and Lo Lieh, in a series of intense poker game standoffs. Famed director of the genre, Wong Jing, also has a guest appearance as one of the Notorious Eight.

programme.title: The Blue and the Black Part 2
programme.desc: Continuing from the first movie, Tang Qi ends her career as a nightclub singer and starts searching battle-scarred China for her lover Chang, who is now entangled with Japanese invaders, communist insurgents, and a warlord's beautiful daughter.

programme.title: Rolls, Rolls, I Love You
programme.desc: Three young men offend a billionaire and are drawn into a high stakes bet. If they win, they get to keep the billionaires Rolls Royce. Otherwise, they will need to pay the rich man fifty thousand dollars! Will the underdogs win the bet?

programme.title: Mr Funny - bone
programme.desc: Join Mr Funny bone in a series of comic vignettes as he attempts to win the heart of a dashing lady. Along for the ride is his loyal sidekick Mr Big Potato, a stout fellow who is forever getting into silly mishaps. The pair gets involved in plenty of shenanigans and gags!

programme.title: Murder Plot
programme.desc: Martial artist Shen Lang is in discussions with kung fu experts from the other six sects to plot the downfall of the traitorous Happy King when his fiance suddenly disrupts them and Shen has to quickly bring her away. As they continue to pursue the Happy King, both Shen and his fiance accidentally fall into a trap set up by the King.

programme.title: The Happy Trio
programme.desc: Ah Chiao, a village girl stranded in the city, befriends a kind-hearted tramp and a retired actor. They are poor but happy, though Ah Chiaos fortune change for the better when she becomes a singer. However, she soon learns that money cannot buy one happiness...

programme.title: Six Assassins
programme.desc: Lord Li Ming is a feudal tyrant who oppresses the people, and even the Emperor who is his brother, cannot stop his evil act. Righteous swordsman Mu poses as Li Mings guard to plan for his assassination. He arrests six assassins who have tried to kill Li Ming, before making them his allies in a secret plot to kill him and end the tyranny.

programme.title: Love without End
programme.desc: Lin Dai stars in this romantic classic as a nightclub singer who falls for a young architect. When he suffers grave financial difficulty, she does the unthinkable to help him.

programme.title: The Thundering Sword
programme.desc: Two disciples, Yu and Zheng, are sent by their master to track down the invincible weapon Thundering Sword to prevent villains from getting it. Yu encounters the daughter of a ruthless clan, Chiao, who is on her way to seek for the sword. They quickly fall for each other, but when Chiao accidentally injures Zheng, things become complicated.

programme.title: My Name Ain't Suzie
programme.desc: Young Mei Li works as a bar girl in Wanchai to make a living. When she meets Jimmy in the bar, she thinks he is her true love and falls crazily in love with him. When Jimmy has to leave, Mei Li is devastated. It is not until she encounters the triad boss Ying that she finally found someone to count on.

programme.title: My Dream Boat
programme.desc: This is a story about the complicated love relationships between a group of young friends who are entangled in a web of love and emotions.

programme.title: The Human Goddess
programme.desc: This is a love story between an alluring fairy, Seventh Sister, who comes down from heaven to experience life in 70s Hong Kong, and a man who is running a debt laden orphanage. A heartless tycoon plans to take over the orphanage for its land but has to deal with Seventh Sisters magical powers as she aims to protect it from falling into his hands!

programme.title: The Water Margin
programme.desc: This is a martial arts epic directed by Chang Cheh. In the Sung Dynasty, the government is run by corrupt officials, so Sung Jiang gathers 108 outlaws at Mount Liang and establishes a band of patriotic heroes to end the repression of brutal overlords.

programme.title: The Adulteress
programme.desc: The film is about the drugged, then disgraced wife of a peddler in the waning days of the Ching Dynasty. To make matters worse, shes soon framed for her husbands murder by her rapist, the son of the local magistrate! And even that is not the end of her woes in this emotional suspense

programme.title: Twin Blades Of Doom
programme.desc: A retired martial artist is forced to return with a vengeance after his family and friends are murdered by the evil Ghost Gang. He decides to challenge the gangs leader to a deadly duel so as to take revenge. Can he defeat the ruthless leader in the end?

programme.title: Lady General Hua Mu-Lan
programme.desc: Mulan disguises herself as a male soldier to replace her aged father in a war against the barbarians. Her courage brings her victory in battles and she was promoted to a general. When Mulan returns home with glory, the chief commander asks her to marry his daughter, forcing Mulan to reveal her true identity.

programme.title: Heaven Sword and Dragon Sabre
programme.desc: In the Yuan Dynasty, martial artists everywhere battle for the Heaven Sword and the Dragon Sabre, as only when these two powerful weapons combine can a secret be revealed to help one become the king of the martial arts world. As Zhang Wu Ji acquires the skills from Nine Yang Scriptures by chance, he is also embroiled in this lengthy battle.

programme.title: The Land of Many Perfumes
programme.desc: Monk Tang San Zang, Monkey, Pigsy and Sha Wu Jing find themselves in Womanland, where women give birth to baby girls by drinking the magical spring water.

programme.title: Wits Of The Brats
programme.desc: Tou Kuan is a wealthy Kwangtung brat with a good kung fu background, he has only one ambition: to pit his wits against three shady masters of the North. The first, conman Che Tsai. The second, a professional romantic dubbed The Terrific. Terrific introduces Tou Kuan to his third rival, Thief Shih San-shou.

programme.title: Empress Wu
programme.desc: Wu Ze Tian is a beautiful and talented concubine of Emperor Tang at age 14. She becomes a nun after he died but has two sons with the new Emperor Tang Gao Zong. The Empress asks Wu to team up with her against Consort Xiao, but is set up and dethroned by Wu, who also kills her two sons. After the Emperors death, Wu becomes the first woman Emperor.

programme.title: Go, Dog. Go! Ep12
programme.desc: Frank and Beans with Chili / Little Hound on the Prairie - Beans is nervous that Frank is starting to make a new best friend, so Beans enlists Tag to help him win Frank back. \ Grandpaw and Grandmaw tell Tag the story of the early days of Pawston. Tags ancestor, Tagatha, built a steam-engine and turned Pawston from a one-house town into a thriving community.

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective Ep12
programme.desc: The Case Of The Dazzle Dragon - Everyone in Fable Fields is very worried that a new Dazzle Dragon has appeared in the land. Big Ears says there's no such thing as a Dragon in Toyland so Noddy decides to investigate. All the evidence seems to lead to a dragon footprints, loud noises and glimpses of shiny scales in the woods but clever Noddy thinks it through and, using his investigating skills of looking and looking again, soon realises that the dragon' isn't a dragon at all! It's the knights out on patrol in their shiny armour and tight formation! Phew! Thanks Noddy!

programme.title: Raa Raa The Noisy Lion Ep12
programme.desc: Hurry Up Raa Raa - Raa Raa has agreed to do too many things with too many people today. Will he be able to do them and keep all his friends happy? More importantly, will it make him happy?

programme.title: Where's Wally? Ep8
programme.desc: Costa Rica... IN COLOR! - When Wizard Whitebeard receives a postcard from Costa Rica, Wenda -- a bird-lover with an encyclopedic knowledge of rare birds -- notices that the birds in the postcard have lost their color! Wally and Wenda head to the Costa Rican rain forest to investigate alongside Wizard Featherbeard.

programme.title: Turbo F.A.S.T. Ep36
programme.desc: Ransom Of White Shadow/Kicked Off - White Shadow is mistaken for a celebrity snail and kidnapped; Tito gets a foosball table which quickly becomes a soccer battle ground.

programme.title: Dinotrux Ep36
programme.desc: Pounder - Ty and the crew must protect the Flatirons from Pounder, a predatory Poundersaurolophus who marks his territory by hammering everything in sight

programme.title: Home: Adventures With Tip And Oh! Ep36
programme.desc: Krebbles Is Real / Tip's Diary - When Oh thinks that his favorite TV show is real, Tip tries to maintain the illusion; When Tip's diary gets boring for Oh, he decides to create drama in her life to liven up his favorite book

programme.title: Spirit Riding Free Ep31
programme.desc: Lucky and the Rough Ride - The PALs join AI and Javier on a mustang drive, but when Javier gets injured, its up to Lucky and Spirit to get him to safety

programme.title: Spirit Riding Free Ep32
programme.desc: Lucky and the Ghostly Gotcha! - When Snips claims not to be afraid of ghosts, the PALs decide to give him a fun Halloween scare hell never forget!

programme.title: Dawn Of The Croods Ep23
programme.desc: Croodtopia / Hand On A Hard Egg - When the adults come down with the sneezles, the kids (including Lerk and Womp) use the chance to create their own society ("you-topia") with no rules, but Eep and Thunk disagree on how to run it/Food is scarce and when a large egg is spotted on the hunting field, Grug, Eep, Snoot, Munk and Squawk call dibbs. It's decided that whoever is tough enough to be the last holding on, wins the food.

programme.title: Dawn Of The Croods Ep24
programme.desc: Disaster Of Puppets / Love Will Eep Us Together - Thunk invents ventriloquism when he tries (and fails) at stand-up comedy, but he gets jealous when Ahhh! Valley thinks the puppet is the real comedian/Eep is determined for two buffalippos to find love when Grug denies her dating privileges.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in Business Ep27
programme.desc: Bossa Nova - After Boss Baby is fired from Baby Corp;he attempts to navigate regular baby life in a Mommy/Daddy/Baby playgroup. Even worse;the playgroups other new member is Mega Fat;whose animatronic stuffie Wagby malfunctions and threatens the safety of the whole group. Meanwhile;Tim does everything he can to avoid doing his homework.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in Business Ep28
programme.desc: The Museum Job - When the crowded bathroom situation at the local museum threatens baby love;Boss Baby leads his new team of playgroup babies on their first missionand then their SECOND mission after a klepto baby in their group swipes a priceless artifact. In a continued attempt to avoid homework;Tim joins Boss Baby on his mission.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in Business Ep29
programme.desc: Ga Ba Goo Ba Ga (The Babblist) - Theres a new babblist in town- someone who claims to understand baby talk. Boss Baby spots this fraud right away;and must debunk his tactics before he scams the playgroup parents. Meanwhile;Tim tries to sell magazines with Boss Babys help.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Paws Of Destiny Ep20
programme.desc: Gongmen City Hustle - Po and the Kids make it to Gongmen City in search of the contact they heard has some info on the dirigible crash. Meanwhile, Xiao, mourning the presumed death of her new panda friends, takes off into the woods and meets a new friend.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Paws Of Destiny Ep21
programme.desc: Night of the White Bone Demon - In a giant sea battle, Po and the Kids manage to escape the pursuing police to make it to Volcano island and get some answers. Empress Xiao begins learning how to defend herself.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Paws Of Destiny Ep22
programme.desc: Rise of the Empress - On the Volcano Island, Po and the Kids are reunited with Li, Grandma, Ping, Rooster, Wing, and Wong, and work together to find out what's really going on the island. Xiao becomes suspicious of some of her royal workers.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep10
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Flustering Mindless Woe of the Flushable Memory Wipes - After being made fun of for sitting in chocolate pudding, George and Harold go into hiding only to come back to find that everybody has forgotten who they are

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep11
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Soggy Salvation of the Swirling Sweatnami - Tired of mean Mr. Krupp, the boys go back in time to prevent him from becoming a bully, but discover that their plan has backfired when they return to the present

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep12
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Sickening Fumes of Smartsy Fartsy - In order to retrieve Mr. Krupps locked up rule book, George and Harold use an invention that ends up turning against them

programme.title: Dragons: Race to the Edge Ep36
programme.desc: Between A Rock And A Hard Place - When Hiccup and the Riders discover that Viggo is using two captured Catastrophic Quakens to build a dragon prison, they must help the dragons escape.

programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep10
programme.desc: Remote Out of Control / Critter Comfort - Biggie takes Branchs superpowered remote but must return it before Branch finds outWhen Poppy builds a new home for a group of cute critters she accidentally attracts their predators.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep36
programme.desc: Get Off My Lawn - When King Julien thinks he's a crime victim, he buys the village self-defense scorpions from a shady dealer, leaving everyone armed and dangerous.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in Business Ep30
programme.desc: The Coo Chi Coup - Boss Baby loves awards- and the Golden Rattle trophy is no exception. When presented with the chance to win an award at a company retreat;he must choose between his pride and his team.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in Business Ep31
programme.desc: Lights, Camera, Org Chart! - Boss Baby creates an org chart to cement his leadership as the Boss of the playgroup babies. However when Bubbeezee photographer Travis Le Duque chooses anyone but Boss for his coverspread;the status quo is upended! Tim continues to fail his class assignment: a model solar system

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in Business Ep32
programme.desc: The Big Break - Boss thought that breaking his arm was painful;but the true pain starts at pediatrician Dr. Kevins jokes. Boss enlists the playgroup babies to defang the doctor of his comedians disease. Tim obsesses about keeping his little brother safe.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Paws Of Destiny Ep20

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep13
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Troublesome Treachery of the Thieving Toot Fairy - George and Harold race against Mr. Krupp to try to get him fired before they get expelled

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep14
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Tenuous Takedown of the Tyrannical Teachertrons - In the season opener, George and Harold have returned to school due to a technicality, but the school has been taken over by Melvin and a cyborg Melvin from the future! Their goal is to make the school extremely difficult by replacing all the teachers with Teachertron robots. Suffering under the new regime and without Mr. Krupp/Captain Underpants on hand to help, the boys hypnotize gym teacher Mr. Meaner and turn him into Sergeant Boxers to fight back.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep15
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Frantic Fury of the Fearsome Furculees - Tired of the Melvins ruling the school, the boys realize that they need Mr. Krupp to make the school at least bearable. Unfortunately, Krupp has run off to Ecuador to look for a fabled fountain. So the boys form the M.I.S.F.A.R.T.S. - Mega Incredible Search Force Adventure Rescue Team Squad - to travel to Ecuador and bring Krupp back, whether he wants it or not.

programme.title: The Adventures Of Puss In Boots Ep51
programme.desc: The Obelisk - When time is running out for Puss to find the Obelisk, he must fight El Moco and finds out who The One from the Great Prophecy is

programme.title: Dragons: Race to the Edge Ep51
programme.desc: Shell Shocked Part 1 - Hiccup doesn't know who to trust when Viggo and Ryker each tell him that the other has gone rogue, and is sidetracked when a new dragon attacks.

programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep51
programme.desc: Tall Tail/BFFF - Creek arrives at a Trolls potluck empty-handed, explaining that a strange creature ate the fondue he meant to bring. The Trolls nod sympathetically, but Branch alone doesnt believe this clearly made-up story. He sets out to prove Creek is a liar./ Branch presents Trolls Village with a time capsule which will survive the ages. The Trolls are excited by the prospect of making friends with future Trolls. Now if only they could agree what should actually go in the time capsule.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep51
programme.desc: I, Maurice - When Maurice learns that he isn't a lemur like everyone else, he sets off on a journey to find his Aye-Aye parents and sister Brosalind

programme.title: Voltron: Legendary Defender Ep25
programme.desc: Best Laid Plans - Team Voltron uses the Black Lion to lure Zarkon into battle

programme.title: Dawn Of The Croods Ep51
programme.desc: Can't Hardly Bait / Crood Detente - After Womp is told he can't attend the upcoming school ceremony, Thunk makes it his personal mission to get Womp to pass every subject before the ceremony; When the Valleyites disagree with letting the Broods move to Ahhh! Valley, Grug throws a giant party to force them to become best friends

programme.title: Spirit Riding Free Ep25
programme.desc: Lucky And Her New Family Part 1 - When El Circo Dos Grillos comes to town, Lucky and Spirit learn circus tricks.

programme.title: Turbo F.A.S.T. Ep25
programme.desc: Hard Luck Hardcase / Bee Story - Hardcase follows the crew to the desert and goes to extreme lengths attempting to finally get his revenge on Turbo. // White Shadow loses his good-luck charm and spirals into a streak of terrible luck and the crew must help him find it before things get any worse.

programme.title: Fifi and the Flowertots Ep77
programme.desc: Fifi's Busy Day - Fifi has been so busy helping everybody else she hasn't had time to tidy her own garden. Bumble asks the other tots to help him tidy his best friend's garden as a surprise for Fifi

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective Ep25
programme.desc: The Case Of The Rules Of The Game - Pat Pat and the pirates have fallen out over who has won board game and as they've lost the rules they can't agree. programme.title: Fifi and the Flowertots Ep64
